data.description: This 3BR/2Bath home features tons of amenities both inside and out.  Features open floor plan, large kitchen with lots of cabinet space, and hardwood/tile floors throughout.  Two standard bedrooms and a flex space that is utilized as a master bedroom gives you tons of space for entertaining friends and family as well as working from home.  Enjoy spending time outside in your above ground pool and privacy fenced deck area.  Two car detached garage is perfect for storing all those extra household items, keeping your car out of the weather, or completing projects.
